snippet.title: Unsigned Character 1.0.4 gameplay
snippet.description:
This is simple gamplay demonstration of Unsigned Charater game.
Unsigned Charater is a dinamic platformer with ASCII-art and procedural generation.
The game available now on android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.cyberslav
Music: https://youtu.be/TNIzvIGGSDY
